edu.illinois.cs.cogcomp.nlp.utilities

Class ParseTreeProperties

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.illinois.cs.cogcomp.nlp.utilities.ParseTreeProperties

  • public class ParseTreeProperties
extends Object
    This class consists of a set of functions of the form "is a label X?", where the label is a node in the parse tree and X could be different linguistic classes, parts of speech, etc. The functions assume that the parse trees are annotated in the Penn Treebank style.

    Most of the information is from the list here.

    Author:
    Vivek Srikumar

    Jan 29, 2009
